"""Test deactivate non existent mfa device raises exception."""
msg = (
    'An error occurred (NoSuchEntity) when calling the DeactivateMFADevice operation: Device with serial number 44324234213 cannot be found.'
    )
self.client.create_user(UserName=self.user)
with pytest.raises(MockBoto3ClientError) as e:
    self.client.deactivate_mfa_device(UserName=self.user, SerialNumber=self
        .serial_number)
assert msg == str(e.value)
mock_iam
